    "en": {
      "title": "SJB Party Leaders to meet today (10)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Samagi Jana Balawegaya (SJB) is scheduled to hold a special party meeting on Sunday (10) morning.",
        "The Secretary-General of the Samagi Jana Balawegaya Ranjith Maddumabandara said that the meeting will be held this morning to establish an all-party government and the emerging political situation.",
        "Chairman of Samagi Jana Balavegaya & Leader of the Opposition Sajith Premadasa",
        "Leader of All Ceylon Makkal Congress Rishad Bathiudeen including party leaders.",
        "Meanwhile, a meeting is planned to be held among the leaders of the 9 parties, including the National Freedom Front on Sunday (10).",
        "Vice President of the Communist Party of Sri Lanka Weerasumana Weerasinghe said that there will be a lengthy discussion about the all-party government."
      ],
